headline.main: Paid Notice: Deaths  MAIDMAN, GAIL ANN LOWE

snippet: MAIDMAN--Gail Ann Lowe. On January 31, 2016 a shooting Star was temporarily eclipsed but one day this exceptional soul and body will be reunited. I will miss the excitement and passion that surrounded Gail. I am grateful for our wonderful children Evan and Starr, their spouses Regina and Jacques, our grandchildren Esme,Teddy and Sterling. Stephen 1/3
